程序包 org.apache.jmeter.gui.action

接口 TreeNodeNamingPolicy

所有已知实现类:
DefaultTreeNodeNamingPolicy
public interface TreeNodeNamingPolicy
Naming policy applied to JMeter Tree nodes :
  • on creation through nameOnCreation(JMeterTreeNode)
  • By applying naming policy on Controller child nodes through resetState(JMeterTreeNode) and rename(JMeterTreeNode, JMeterTreeNode, int)
从以下版本开始:
3.2
